@Node KAJ "Project"

Amistart is unique utility program in nice graphic environment     
( 126 colors in main screen ). Amistart is program for all these 
Amiga freaks out there that want to have nice boot picture, no 
click,..., nice commodity programs in their WBStartup and so 
on. With this program you can and will have all this and much 
more. You can also read info about each program included in 
English and Slovene language and install every program you 
like with simple point and click procedure or ( in cases of big 
programs ) unarchive program and then install it from 
Workbench.

@EndNode

@Node INS "AMISTART"

@{b}  INSTALATION AND USAGE@{ub}

Before you start the program, you must run installer provided 
with this program. Then reboot computer and start the program 
( click on the icon called  AMISTART). Problem info : 
miro.hacek@uni-lj.si

@EndNode

@Node TEZ "AMISTART"

@{b} POSSIBLE PROBLEMS@{ub}

Program runs on all AGA Amigas with 6Mb RAM ( I think 4Mb 
will also be enough ). You will also need about 3Mb free space 
on your hard drive. Tested on 020/28 and 030/50 with 4Mb 
RAM. If program fails to run, please try xtra-libs ( math libs; you 
will find them in Amistart/Sys directory ), but before you do that, 
please backup your original libs.

@EndNode

